---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components'
---
<section class="relative py-16 sm:py-20 lg:py-24 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-slate-800">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
    <div class="mb-12 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-tighter tracking-tighter mb-4 font-heading">
        Secure Your Digital Identity
      </h2>
      <p class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
        Your domain is your online home. Let's find the perfect address for your web presence.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12">
      <form class="relative flex">
        <input
          type="text"
          placeholder="Enter your dream domain name"
          class="w-full px-6 py-4 rounded-l-full border-2 border-r-0 border-green-500 focus:border-green-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-green-500 dark:bg-slate-700 dark:border-green-400 dark:text-white text-lg outline-none"
        />
        <button
          type="submit"
          class="px-8 py-4 rounded-r-full bg-green-500 text-white font-bold text-lg hover:bg-green-600 transition duration-300 flex items-center justify-center min-w-[140px] border-2 border-green-500 hover:border-green-600"
        >
          <Icon name="tabler:search" class="w-6 h-6 mr-2" />
          Discover
        </button>
      </form>
    </div>
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Your Domain, Your Empire</h3>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <Icon name="tabler:lock-open" class="w-12 h-12 mb-4 mx-auto text-primary" />
          <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Freedom of Choice</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
            At WebCraft, we believe in <span class="font-semibold text-primary">your freedom</span>. Purchase your domain through us or choose your preferred provider. No lock-ins, just possibilities.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <Icon name="tabler:building" class="w-12 h-12 mb-4 mx-auto text-primary" />
          <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Your Digital Real Estate</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
            Owning your domain is like owning prime real estate in the digital world. <span class="font-semibold text-primary">Don't rent, own your online identity</span>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12">
        <h4 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Trusted Domain Providers</h4>
        <p class="mb-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
          While you're free to choose any registrar, here are our top picks for reliable domain registration:
        </p>
        <div class="flex justify-center space-x-6">
          <a href="https://www.domains.co.za" class="flex items-center bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 px-4 py-2 rounded-full shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition duration-300" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <Icon name="tabler:star" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-yellow-500" />
            <span class="font-semibold">domains.co.za</span>
          </a>
          <a href="https://www.godaddy.co.za" class="flex items-center bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 px-4 py-2 rounded-full shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition duration-300" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <Icon name="tabler:world" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-primary" />
            <span class="font-semibold">godaddy.co.za</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-8 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-slate-500">
        Remember, your choice of domain provider doesn't affect our ability to craft an outstanding website for you. We're here to build your digital dreams, wherever they're hosted.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
